title: BRAND-NEW 1 BR Apt Available! Apply Today Before It’s Gone!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY – our new rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your brand-new home!', '1500 Nicollet – A one-of-a-kind Twin Cities apartment living community!', 'We’ve designed these apartment homes with you in mind and are offering smart layouts, quality materials, and luxurious amenities seldom found in this price range.', 'Enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location.', 'These one, two and three bedroom apartments feature open & spacious floor plans, a full-size washer & dryer, energy efficient lighting & appliances, large windows providing tons of natural sunlight, and individually controlled heating & air conditioning.', 'Make 1500 Nicollet your home today!', 'Specific layouts & square footage may vary according to specific floor plan types.', 'All finishes & appliances are the same in every home.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- WaterSense Plumbing Fixtures', '- Individually Controlled Heating & Air-Conditioning', '- Huge Exterior Courtyard Area', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Modern Interior Home Design', '- Gorgeous Kitchen Cabinetry with Quartz Countertops', '- On-Site Fitness Center & Yoga Studio', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', 'See Respective Floor Plan Info -', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 11:00AM-6:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', '1500 Nicollet', '1500 Nicollet Ave.', 'South', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55403', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'uGpxY2D4zFla']
